Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a psychiatrist for the last 35 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a psychoanalyst, nutritionist, researcher into brain chemistry and its relationship to nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the last seven years I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and its application to spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this series we are looking at the application of the knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,derived from this study of the nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to human problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In this particular talk today we'll be talking about sexuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about the difference between sex and making love,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,between high and low energy sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,how to transcend being guilty and at the effect of social programming about sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,how to experience it from the heart instead of just from the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,how to make it an uplifting and grand experience
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than one of manipulation and control,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how to get out of the energy interactions which result in impotence and frigidity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and sexual dysfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask the question, does God approve of sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is sex all over with advancing age?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Does middle age mean you're over the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These and other questions as we address it from the viewpoint of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking from that position,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of body, mind and spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,about which we have heard so much in the field of holistic health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a slogan? Is that a catchphrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean, body, mind and spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is spirit anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something we can experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an energy to that that we can discover through our own inner research
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and to our own inner experiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be talking today about our own inner experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,subtle states,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,inner awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the part they play in this important area of human behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we do that, we want to get into the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of the relationship between body and mind and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to review where it is that human experience is experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,talk a little bit about consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,demystify it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn it into something understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To help us to do that, we'll be referring to a chart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,on the blackboard here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've used in others of this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,referring to the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a mathematical model that has come out of our research,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which is very helpful in understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of the relationship between body, mind and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll review briefly what is that relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And we begin by looking at the fact that the body itself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're talking about sexuality, everybody automatically thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the body and its allure and all the physicality of form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And astonishingly enough, when we look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we realize that the body itself is in ascension.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, it cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The arm cannot experience its armness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The leg cannot experience its legness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else, something greater than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,has to take place before experience happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So the body is experienced through sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What we experience is not the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but the sensations of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,where it is in space and where it is in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensations themselves cannot really experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to be experienced in something larger,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at it carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we realize we are not experiencing the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not really experiencing the sensations of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're experiencing what is going on in mind about the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself, curiously enough, cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought doesn't experience its thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling doesn't experience its feelingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something larger than mind has to be present,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is unchanging in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what is going on in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason we become aware of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is because of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a much larger energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Than that of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're aware of what is going on in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then, because of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind is telling us what is going on in emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts, sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensations are telling us what is going on in body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what we're experiencing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then, is always going on in the field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is like an invisible screen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that is really located everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself is really unaware
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is happening within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of something infinitely larger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,than even consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of awareness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has no dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no locality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we're experiencing experience, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,within the field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in handling human problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,behavioral problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding human behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can address it, then, directly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,by going
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to its experience within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is more powerful and more dominant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we can handle problems that seem to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,arising in the body by handling them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on the level of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what we'll be doing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be looking at human experience and events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll be seeing that events are one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but how we choose to be with them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not be able to determine or control
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or choose the events that occur in our life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can determine how we wish to be with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the experience of how to be with that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is perhaps more important than the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know that in a certain mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a trivial, you know, an irritation may be trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that in another mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that same event can be aggravating
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or even send us into a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, how we are with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and that brings up the whole concept of energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field, the position from which
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we're coming about a situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we are holding our own existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the importance of all events
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of the context
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,created by our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll be referring to this chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which we referred to in other talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we have these levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and each of these levels
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,has been calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as to their relative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of that energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated mathematically,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which gives us an understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in our left brain way of understanding things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of them has a direction of an energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it is negative or positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of these energy fields come emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which we'll be referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,comes a way of viewing the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a view of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of relating to that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which is greater than our individual self,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and a process that is going on in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll pull this all together then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll pull this all together
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as we address the questions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of high energy sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is coming out of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is coming out of our way of being in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and low energy sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is localized in a physical kind of an experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,about which society has had so much to say over the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How to resolve the conflicts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that come out of holding it from that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see that man's conflict about sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of his position about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,how he perceives it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what it means to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Problems are best solved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,not on the level at which they appear to be occurring,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but on the next level above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we're not going to be talking about philosophy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be talking about clinical experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you can verify through your own experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,through human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to look at the area of problems
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from a level that is above the problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So problems are best solved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by transcending them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and looking at them from a higher viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in which very often
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's a shift of point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem automatically resolves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or we see that there wasn't any to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we want to go back to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the difference between high and low energy sex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and see how what man considers sexual problems
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are coming really out of an energy field itself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and how we can change our position with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In general, when people talk about sex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they are referring to a type of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but they are talking considerably
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,about an energy field which everybody presumes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and which Madison Avenue plays on called desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What they are talking about is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain way of looking at things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the overcoming of a frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the overcoming of lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the withholding of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the manipulation of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the gratifying of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the using it as trade in relationships,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the allure, the price,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the value added to this allure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and to the physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So in general, man is talking about physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And from there, because of the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then he gets into the field of morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so morality is coming out of physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,holding sexuality from the physical level,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from the lower energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we have the story of the Garden of Eden
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and what happens in the Garden of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens in the Garden of Eden
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the man and the woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in a very high energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,eat of the tree of knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,eat of the tree of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They buy into a world of duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the world of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In lovingness, lovingness just is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart doesn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart just knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart is with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In eating of the tree of right and wrong, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and good and evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what happened is they saw themselves as bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They came down into guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, guilt is at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So from a high state of joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that state of lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite being with life out of joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond right and wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't even arise,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,they fell into a field
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in which they were looking at the body as a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As a body, they then became conscious of its bodiness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that arose man's sexual problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So whether it's historically an event or not is immaterial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychologically, it is an event that has happened to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the problems that man calls sexual
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,are really due to a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a point of view about physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing sexuality as a physical phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,being run by the desire of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the opposite side of the coin of desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so sexuality is then characterized by desiring this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's characterized by aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's characterized by avoiding the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting nothing to do with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,taking a moralistic position about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is now superior to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior to seeing it as an animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,physical function.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It even degrades that which is the animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and calls it animal as though
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the animal world which is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and was created by God
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is somehow immoral,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,calling it animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the difficulty then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty is not in sexuality at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty is within consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how mind is holding what sexuality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's arising out of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,how in consciousness the mind is seeing sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it defines these relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We know from our study of these fields of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything we call courage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in an energy field of 200
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where we see that this arrow is neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's no longer negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we see everything from this level down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as positions of victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as positions of coming from lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, guilt and apathy and grief and fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,desire, anger, pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,are all coming from positions of lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of not having wholeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,not being at one with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, holding sexuality then from the physical level,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,dividing it according to gender
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,into maleness and femaleness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a feeling of separation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that separation then comes desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that comes frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the frustration comes anger and resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of all that comes fear and grief and apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so some people are into guilt over sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,some people are into apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness, lack of desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and some people are into grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,some people are into fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,people are into desiringness and wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and being run by that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and anger over that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or the endless pridefulness about sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the strutting one's macho image
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or the sticking out of one's feminine attributes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in a prideful and tantalizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,seductive kind of controlling,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,manipulating, exploiting kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see the marketing industry do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,use this desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,use this frustration, this lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this feeling of separation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to control people and manipulate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the pretty girl sitting on the hood of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, what has a car got to do with a pretty girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's trying to connect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get this car, if I get this shampoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if I get this hairdo, if I wear this perfume,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will overcome this separation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,between myself and that which I desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that point of view then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is creating an endless painfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,an endless source of suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the suffering takes various forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's impotence or frigidity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or satiriasis, whatever the form may take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out of holding sexuality from that view,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,from its physicalness, from its desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from its wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see how therefore one is run by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We see one nature of this energy field of desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotions accompanying that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are wantingness, cravingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to be addicted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know people who become addicted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexuality is what runs them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless going to bed with everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that is available.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The needing to prove one's desirability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The needing to prove something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see over on the right hand side
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on this energy level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called entrapment, entrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Within consciousness, on this energy level,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,once you want something,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that wanting begins to run you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The desiringness wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The wantingness runs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Temporary gratification.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the negativity of this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which is endlessly frustrating,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,endlessly wanting, endlessly craving,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the person still remains entrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no feeling of finality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no feeling of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that happiness does not occur
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get up to an energy field of about 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore trying to find happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,through the endless creation and satisfaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the cycling of this desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the release of the frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally frustration feels good
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when you temporarily satisfy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good when you stop banging your head
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is not the same thing as happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The desiringness, the cravingness continues on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of this then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because of this physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that all the moral questions arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,why does morality address itself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to this kind of an energy field?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it called carnal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is called carnal because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it is like lower energy sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of the lower energy fields of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,being held in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in a lower viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the whole question of morality
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then addresses itself really to that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which is carnality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Carnality in this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,looking down on one's animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of prizing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being grateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of saying it is beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it is being downgraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which is intrinsically beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when it is not judged
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is held in a degrading manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How to get off this cycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,how to experience sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,from a much different energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How to get released from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will take us back into
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a discussion then of how
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,how to let go being at the effect of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let go being run by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the cycling of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How to be with sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it is experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as a totally different experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When we hold it and look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all the questions and problems
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,now disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as withholding,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,frustration, being run by desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,going into anger and resentment over that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,going into a feeling of lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If the desire is not fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then what comes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What comes up is a fear that it won't be fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a grief that it hasn't been,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,an apathy, an anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a frustration, a self-blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that at the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt is accompanied by self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that holding sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from this level leads to a view
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world of sin and suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of hopelessness, of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And sexuality, the whole subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to guard our children from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes competitive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when sex is used in a seductive manner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in a manipulative power field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have its use as a symbol of status.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One's sexual attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then becomes a status symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And the adornment of the human body,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera, becomes a symbol of status,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,another way of controlling and manipulating
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to influence one's sense of self-worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The worry and the anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the wantingness, the resentment, the hatreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see that sexuality based on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy field often leads to hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have the stabbings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the violent murders based on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that infatuation, that seduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the manipulation of one by another
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the triangulations of these situations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the unconscious exploitations that are going on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,based on this desiringness, this attractiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the denial about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we get up to pridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the morality about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we get into contempt, we get into denial,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we get into religious conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we get into people who hold all sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from a contemptuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,looking down their nose at it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as though anybody who indulges in that kind of activity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,must be coming from a low animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They presume that everyone else is run by it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same way that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,People who hold contempt for it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are projecting their own way of being with it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,onto others and saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't they carnal, aren't they animal, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let go of that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll contrast that with a high energy sex
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with a different energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with a different way of being with it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that then transcends all these problems
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of competition, frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of fright and guilt and regret
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and worry and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just imagine, how can you enjoy yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in a human endeavor that is taking place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in this whole energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in which secretly you feel really
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that God is probably going to punish you for it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because the view of God coming out of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,these energy fields is punitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You are certainly separated from Him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you get any enjoyment or happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,very likely at the end there's going to be retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people can't stand the intensity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of this conflict between
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the driving biologic urge,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the psychological need and religion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and so they just split out of it all together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and jump into atheism
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which just handles the whole thing that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One has to either let go of one's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,view of God and religion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or let go of one's sexuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so for some people it is an impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,conflict to resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and many people end up as atheistic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's no way they can handle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,their humanness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and also their views of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we move out of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we move away from being run by that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,this behavior, these experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different energy field?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll contrast it with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy field of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as an expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean sexuality as an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sense of aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of being with the truth of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to experience that concept,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of an experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to let go of this lower
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in which sex is experienced really
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as a local physical phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,sit down and ask them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if I ask them in the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,what is sexual experience to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is primarily a local physical phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you get all kinds of preoccupation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with anatomy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,immense preoccupation with their fitness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sexual partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and women's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Focusing on the physical attributes of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And along with the physicalness of it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,goes emotionality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,emotionality, sentimentality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And emotionality plus physicality then
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the expression of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The mad passionate embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the expression of the emotionality
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of wantingness and desiringness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.81,0:24:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh how I want you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.81,0:24:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I crave you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.81,0:24:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,oh how I must have you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the thrill of all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.45,0:24:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is what the movies portray, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let go of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of an experience is possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of an experience is possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.44,0:24:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll contrast with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of an experience would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.44,0:24:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was no longer local,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was no longer a negative energy field of 125?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.44,0:25:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if it happened out of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.44,0:25:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,out of a positive energy field of 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.44,0:25:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the space of being with the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.44,0:25:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the truth of that which you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,First we'll have to talk about how to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of this energy field then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.15,0:25:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How to not be run by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.15,0:25:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How to experience sex
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.15,0:25:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's extremely appropriate,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when there is no conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.15,0:25:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we let go of this cravingness?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.34,0:25:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If this energy field is what is causing all the problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then how can we transcend it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.34,0:25:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can experience it from a much higher level?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use a technique which is worked with weight problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which is worked with pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.17,0:25:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which is worked with illnesses of a great variety of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.17,0:25:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The basic principle works the same
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.17,0:25:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what we apply it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.17,0:25:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is when the energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when the feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.24,0:25:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when the expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.24,0:25:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when the desire comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:25:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what we do is we let go labeling it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.24,0:26:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or calling it anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We let go of the images and the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.72,0:26:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead we allow the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.72,0:26:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of what it is, the sensations of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.16,0:26:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.16,0:26:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We let go resisting them
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.16,0:26:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and as we do we let them run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we letting run out?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.16,0:26:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're letting run out the energy field of desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.16,0:26:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of cravingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.16,0:26:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that thing that seems to be coming out of your solar plexus
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.16,0:26:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.16,0:26:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.16,0:26:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you will realize it is not a pleasurable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.16,0:26:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a pleasurable experience
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand there in this door window
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at what is inside
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with a feeling of wanting, wanting, frustrated craving.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.16,0:26:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at it and cancel the content of what,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.16,0:26:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's diamonds, a fur coat,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or someone else's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.16,0:26:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you will realize that the experience itself is unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.16,0:27:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To want and not have is unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.16,0:27:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To want and not have at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To want a steak and smell it cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.16,0:27:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but not being able to eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.16,0:27:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is really frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.16,0:27:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hold a steak in front of a dog's nose
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.16,0:27:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and just don't allow him to eat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what is he experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.16,0:27:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he experiencing happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.16,0:27:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he glad to be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.16,0:27:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep it up long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up with anger and rage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.52,0:27:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,at the frustration of this desiringness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.52,0:27:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a pleasant feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.52,0:27:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not that which contributes to sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The illusion is it is the desire
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.52,0:27:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that brings sex into my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.52,0:27:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The wanting and the desiring of it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.52,0:27:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is why I get to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.68,0:27:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the opposite is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.68,0:27:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the wantingness and the desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.68,0:27:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which is blocking its coming into your life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.68,0:27:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and your full enjoyment of it when it is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.41,0:27:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go of this craving and this desiring then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.41,0:28:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what eventually happens is all the suppressed desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.41,0:28:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have repressed and suppressed in this lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.41,0:28:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and shoved down like a tank of compressed gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.41,0:28:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure of this comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.41,0:28:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you allow it to just be released,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.41,0:28:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,allow it to flow through you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.41,0:28:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,without doing anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.41,0:28:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,without opposing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.41,0:28:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,let go resisting experiencing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.41,0:28:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is it begins to decompress.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.41,0:28:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, because there is a limited quantity of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it finally stops altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to your life then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.60,0:28:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when the cravingness, the desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.60,0:28:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the obsession, the compulsion,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.60,0:28:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the addiction to the wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.60,0:28:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the cravingness of this physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.60,0:28:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sexuality happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.60,0:28:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is you have peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shocking thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.60,0:28:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there was a desiringness, a cravingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.60,0:28:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a wantingness, a frustration, a feeling of lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.60,0:28:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a feeling of not havingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.60,0:29:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a feeling of low self-esteem
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.60,0:29:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is not being gratified,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.60,0:29:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,instead now you have a peacefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.60,0:29:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing just doesn't arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.60,0:29:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing happens when you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.60,0:29:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,your hunger and your craving and your desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.60,0:29:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and your appetiting all the time for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.60,0:29:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That greediness finally lets go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.60,0:29:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we're talking really about a variety of greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.60,0:29:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not even talking about sex, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.60,0:29:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Greed can be a greed for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be a greed for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.60,0:29:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But the nature of it still,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.60,0:29:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of what the world calls sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.60,0:29:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a greediness, a wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.60,0:29:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a forever desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.60,0:29:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which runs people, runs their whole life, dominates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.48,0:29:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of this, there is an inner state of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.48,0:29:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,an inner state of serenity,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.48,0:29:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as though the whole question has been handled,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.48,0:29:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as though it's no longer a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the problem now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.48,0:29:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It no longer drives you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.84,0:30:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It no longer insults you, insults your integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.84,0:30:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer have to sell yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.93,0:30:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The person doesn't feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.93,0:30:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to now barter and trade their body
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.93,0:30:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and their sexual expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.93,0:30:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a give and trade, an endless bargaining
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.03,0:30:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes on between men and women and sexual partners
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.03,0:30:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for those that choose the same sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.03,0:30:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The tantalizing with it, the withholding,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.06,0:30:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the gift of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.06,0:30:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've paid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.06,0:30:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid for your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.06,0:30:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now give me your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.06,0:30:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless trade-off and bargaining comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.06,0:30:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One is now free of being manipulated by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.06,0:30:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not forget that when we manipulate others,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.44,0:30:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we are equally manipulated in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.44,0:30:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When we let go, manipulating through this sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.54,0:30:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this variety of sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.54,0:30:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that means we cannot be manipulated by it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.54,0:30:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So we become freer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.54,0:31:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, once you are unattached,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.54,0:31:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we move into the field of facing and coping with this problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,our willingness to face and cope with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.54,0:31:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens is we become unattached,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.54,0:31:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we become released.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.15,0:31:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here we were entrapped and up here we are released.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.18,0:31:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the release state?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.18,0:31:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't moved up to love yet, but we're on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.18,0:31:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the release state?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.18,0:31:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The release state means that I am so free of that now
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.18,0:31:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that if it happens in my life, that's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.18,0:31:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it doesn't happen in my life, I don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.18,0:31:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like if we have steak for dinner, fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.24,0:31:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we don't, that's okay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.24,0:31:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have beans and salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.24,0:31:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So there may be a choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.76,0:31:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but the first time we are now at the level
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.76,0:31:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of being able to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.76,0:31:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not run by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.76,0:31:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not run by this manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every billboard doesn't send us to the store
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.76,0:31:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to buy the chewing gum or whatever the pretty girl is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.76,0:31:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.76,0:32:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our willingness now to handle this, to transcend it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.76,0:32:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,moves us up to an acceptance
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.76,0:32:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and allows us now to begin to feel adequate and confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.76,0:32:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel adequate because somehow there's an inner knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.85,0:32:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that somehow the question has been finally answered in our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.85,0:32:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We know we're never going to be at the effect of that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.85,0:32:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really going to run us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.85,0:32:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's a certain sense of freedom comes in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.85,0:32:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So where there was frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.85,0:32:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there's now freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.85,0:32:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore we begin to feel adequate as a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.85,0:32:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and far more confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.85,0:32:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're willing then,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.85,0:32:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to begin to move into a lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.85,0:32:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The world begins to seem more friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.85,0:32:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See, when sex is something you bargain,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.85,0:32:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's something that your status depends on,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.85,0:32:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's your stock and trade in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.85,0:32:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it hardly looks like a friendly world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.85,0:32:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It really looks like a world of competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.85,0:32:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the world begins to look more okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.85,0:33:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to look friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to look harmonious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.85,0:33:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to enjoy the opportunities for sexual expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.85,0:33:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move in and out of acceptance then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.75,0:33:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptance, we move into an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.75,0:33:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,where we're beginning to approach happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.78,0:33:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy field which calibrates mathematically at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.78,0:33:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as compared to 0 for death, 30 for guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.78,0:33:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ones we've talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.78,0:33:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.78,0:33:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of mellowness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.78,0:33:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of feeling really good about ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.78,0:33:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and with our behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.84,0:33:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This lovingness then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of nurture and support,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.84,0:33:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to forgive,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to experience our own being
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.94,0:33:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with this field of behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,from a whole different point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.94,0:33:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy field then resolves all the problems
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.94,0:33:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that arise in this lower energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.94,0:33:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.40,0:34:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is experienced in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.40,0:34:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's say for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.40,0:34:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if your consciousness was colored blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.40,0:34:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then everything you're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.40,0:34:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in your blue consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.40,0:34:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're experiencing is blueness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.40,0:34:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If your consciousness is colored pink, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.47,0:34:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,then all your experience
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be experienced as pinkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.47,0:34:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that this negativity then colors
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.60,0:34:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole experience of one's sexual life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.60,0:34:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's characteristic of these lower energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.69,0:34:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're coming from a lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.69,0:34:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.69,0:34:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is that everything is experienced as giving and getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.69,0:34:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, wanting means what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.69,0:34:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the exchange of giving and getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.69,0:34:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you hear expressions about one's sexual life
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.69,0:34:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,then in these lower energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.69,0:34:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of, did you get it last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.69,0:34:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's worrying about whether she's going to give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.69,0:34:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worrying about whether he's going to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.69,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The adolescent boys get together in the locker room
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the question is, did you get it last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.69,0:35:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move up out of the lower energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.33,0:35:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of giving and getting,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.33,0:35:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you move into the middle energy fields of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, people are preoccupied
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.33,0:35:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with the doingness of sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.33,0:35:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, let's do it is the expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.33,0:35:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.33,0:35:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, this style of doing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.88,0:35:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the preoccupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.88,0:35:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we have the endless,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.88,0:35:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,sex manuals all talking about doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.88,0:35:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They, of course, throw in some love,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.88,0:35:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the more modern ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.88,0:35:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice to have love there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That should alter the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.88,0:35:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's considered to be romanticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.00,0:35:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Romanticism and something that women require
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to have happy sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.00,0:35:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are supposed to have an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.23,0:35:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which she calls lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.23,0:35:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which generally is coming out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.23,0:35:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,plus sentimentality and emotionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.23,0:35:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So she can now hold it from the viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.23,0:36:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of what she considers lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.23,0:36:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so she can then indulge her desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.23,0:36:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without experiencing guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.23,0:36:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field then of doingness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.23,0:36:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the middle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with how well you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.48,0:36:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people then become anxious
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.48,0:36:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,about their performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.48,0:36:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If sex is something you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.48,0:36:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then you should do it well in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.48,0:36:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we have the whole idea
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.48,0:36:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of competitive performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.48,0:36:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of competitiveness and performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.48,0:36:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of performance anxiety comes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.48,0:36:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,frigidity and lack of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.48,0:36:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the various forms of impotence
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.48,0:36:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in which there is the anxiety about doingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.48,0:36:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,performance anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.52,0:36:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he like the way I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.52,0:36:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she like the way I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I satisfied the other person?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.52,0:36:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes sort of athletics,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.52,0:36:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a refined athletics.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.52,0:36:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So from getting,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.09,0:36:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,from having,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.09,0:36:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,giving and getting,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.09,0:37:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we move up to doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.09,0:37:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And now what happens when we start moving up,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.09,0:37:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when we let go of all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.09,0:37:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're no longer run by that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.09,0:37:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then it becomes a way of how to be with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.09,0:37:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes of how you are with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.09,0:37:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of sharing your being with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.16,0:37:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't what you give and get.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.16,0:37:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't how you perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.16,0:37:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as though there's a rating scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.16,0:37:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know he got 82 on his doing list
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.16,0:37:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.16,0:37:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a way of being with the person
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.60,0:37:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the whole barter system falls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.60,0:37:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole performance system falls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this way of being with somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.60,0:37:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer viewed from a lower position,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.60,0:37:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole question of guilt falls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All the moralistic questions are now answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.60,0:37:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To come from being with that other person,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.60,0:37:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with who they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.60,0:37:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,now the desire is to be with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.60,0:38:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It means a connection within the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.60,0:38:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the opening up of a space,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.60,0:38:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of being with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.60,0:38:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See the fear arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.31,0:38:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,well if I let go of my desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.31,0:38:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if I let go of that wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.31,0:38:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't that mean that it will disappear from my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.31,0:38:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Research and experience and clinical experience
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.31,0:38:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,has shown that the opposite is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.31,0:38:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That the letting go of that desire
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.31,0:38:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that the letting go of the desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.31,0:38:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.31,0:38:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which in itself in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.31,0:38:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,sets up a resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.31,0:38:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See that which we want and desire
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.31,0:38:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,sets up in the other person a resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the salesman comes on to you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.50,0:38:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in his salesman style,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.85,0:38:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you know he's going to want to sell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.88,0:38:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you get that he wants to sell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.88,0:38:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what comes up in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.88,0:38:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you going to resist that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.92,0:38:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the pressure and the resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.92,0:38:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the counterbalances,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.92,0:38:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which are going on in these lower energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.92,0:39:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in being with the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.92,0:39:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then out of a lack of,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.92,0:39:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a non-existence of desiringness and wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.92,0:39:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.56,0:39:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've created this space then
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.56,0:39:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.56,0:39:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which are coming down through the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.56,0:39:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,through the energy of life itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.56,0:39:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to express themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.56,0:39:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in that way which is most appropriate to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.56,0:39:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of the energy coming
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.56,0:39:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,up,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.56,0:39:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the so-called Kundalini energy coming up the spine,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.56,0:39:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being run by the entrapment of that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.56,0:39:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in the body's lower energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.56,0:39:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the energy field of life itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.56,0:39:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is life itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.56,0:39:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,coming down through the body
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.56,0:39:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and opening up through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.45,0:39:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go of the lower energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.45,0:39:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,opens the way for the higher energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.00,0:39:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The opening up of joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.00,0:39:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the joyfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.00,0:39:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.00,0:39:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to express itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.00,0:39:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.00,0:40:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens in the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.00,0:40:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of performance
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.00,0:40:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is the desire to bring happiness and pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.00,0:40:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and to support the other person's experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.00,0:40:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.00,0:40:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to the love making.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.00,0:40:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See, no longer is it worried about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.00,0:40:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.00,0:40:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer is it worried about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.00,0:40:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,morality,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.00,0:40:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer is it struggling
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.00,0:40:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with moralistic questions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.00,0:40:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because those have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.00,0:40:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with being stuck in desiringness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.00,0:40:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The negativity that arises out of that field
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.00,0:40:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically brings other negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.06,0:40:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the negative thoughts are,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.06,0:40:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.06,0:40:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.06,0:40:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I being used?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.06,0:40:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I being exploited?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.06,0:40:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.06,0:40:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I built correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.06,0:40:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I in the right position?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.06,0:40:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I being like it's done in the movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.06,0:40:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I doing it like it is in the performance manuals?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.06,0:40:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And there isn't much space there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.96,0:40:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for the enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.96,0:40:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't much space there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.96,0:40:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Space there for the love of sexuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.96,0:41:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, what happens when you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.96,0:41:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the desiring of sexuality?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.96,0:41:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.02,0:41:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, if I let go of my desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.02,0:41:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.02,0:41:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.02,0:41:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.02,0:41:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens with letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.02,0:41:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the desiringness for it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.02,0:41:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is a love for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.02,0:41:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A love for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.02,0:41:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A love for a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.02,0:41:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when you let go desiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.08,0:41:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to own something,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.08,0:41:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.08,0:41:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.08,0:41:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to master it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.08,0:41:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.08,0:41:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to clutch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.08,0:41:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.08,0:41:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you want to desire it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.08,0:41:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.08,0:41:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,even when you get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.08,0:41:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what comes up next
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.08,0:41:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is the fear of losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.08,0:41:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the diamond bracelet,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.08,0:41:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the diamond bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.08,0:41:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What comes up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.08,0:41:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.08,0:41:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the obvious thing that comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.08,0:41:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the weeping and the wailing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.08,0:41:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when that which has been desired and gotten
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.08,0:41:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is eventually lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.08,0:41:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of losing comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.82,0:41:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When we move into the energy field then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.82,0:41:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.82,0:41:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.82,0:41:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what takes the place of desiring
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.82,0:42:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and wanting sex
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.82,0:42:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is the loving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.82,0:42:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to love sex for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.82,0:42:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.82,0:42:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,love is non-judgmental.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.82,0:42:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.82,0:42:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It sees its naturalness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.82,0:42:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's aware of the intrinsic innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.82,0:42:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It watches the animals now
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.82,0:42:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.82,0:42:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It sees the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.82,0:42:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the grace
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.82,0:42:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the animalness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.82,0:42:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's out of a negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.98,0:42:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,condemning,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.98,0:42:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,moralistic energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you can then begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.98,0:42:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the incredible beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.98,0:42:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.98,0:42:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,indeed the sacredness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.98,0:42:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of this expression of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.98,0:42:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The expression of one's aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.98,0:42:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The thrill and joy and experience
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy field of one's aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.98,0:42:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to love sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.98,0:42:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so now we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.98,0:42:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the sexuality of love
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.98,0:42:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love of sex
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.98,0:42:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as an expression of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.98,0:43:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.24,0:43:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of desire itself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.24,0:43:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is, as we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.30,0:43:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we saw that desire has sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.46,0:43:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.46,0:43:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.52,0:43:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to bring in the propensity
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.52,0:43:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of these negative energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.52,0:43:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.52,0:43:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that it isn't just the desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.52,0:43:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems to bring with it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.52,0:43:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.52,0:43:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes us prone to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.52,0:43:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The guilt and the apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.52,0:43:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.52,0:43:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.52,0:43:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.52,0:43:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the pridefulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.52,0:43:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the anxiety about performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.88,0:43:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're free of desire, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.64,0:43:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we're released from guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.64,0:43:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're released from remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.64,0:43:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're released from anticipation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.64,0:43:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of maybe it won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.64,0:43:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these energies arising then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.64,0:43:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,almost en masse,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.64,0:43:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,almost as a unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.68,0:43:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We let go worrying about
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.68,0:43:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going to happen with sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.68,0:43:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as we get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.68,0:43:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole question of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.68,0:43:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are you over the hill
