Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.34,0:45:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.34,0:45:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.34,0:45:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so in how to be with that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.34,0:45:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what is attractive now
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.34,0:45:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is that person's energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.34,0:45:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.34,0:45:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body comes and goes.
