Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.52,0:46:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,their energy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.52,0:46:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.52,0:46:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is our own energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.52,0:46:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexual attractiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.52,0:46:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as amazing as it may sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.52,0:46:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,does not exist in the outer world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.52,0:46:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is something that you
