Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.52,0:46:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexual energy is something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.52,0:46:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that you own.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.52,0:46:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you consider
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.52,0:46:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to be attractive
