Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.72,0:47:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,these are only projections
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.72,0:47:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of our own images
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.72,0:47:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are holding within.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.72,0:47:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we haven't even owned it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.84,0:47:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
