Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.52,0:50:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience that person
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.52,0:50:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.68,0:50:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The spontaneity of it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.68,0:50:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,arises out of the space,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.68,0:50:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.68,0:50:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but out of the sense of aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.68,0:50:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of being
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.68,0:50:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with the space of that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.32,0:50:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a diffuse overall experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.32,0:50:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of a local anatomical experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.32,0:50:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,limited anatomically
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.32,0:50:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to a small area of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.32,0:51:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanied by emotionality,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.32,0:51:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.32,0:51:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there is an overall aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.32,0:51:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.32,0:51:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,encompasses and surrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.32,0:51:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.32,0:51:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.32,0:51:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is arising out of the energy field itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.32,0:51:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.32,0:51:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with the personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.32,0:51:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have nothing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.32,0:51:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with that solar plexus wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.32,0:51:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.32,0:51:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or that genital excitability
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.32,0:51:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which comes out of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.32,0:51:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and its frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.32,0:51:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead is the joy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.32,0:51:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of being with that energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.32,0:51:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the gratefulness for the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.32,0:51:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.32,0:51:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the high joy and pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.32,0:51:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is a sense of alness,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.32,0:51:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of completeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.32,0:51:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very moment
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.90,0:51:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that this desiringness arises
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.90,0:51:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in this type of energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.90,0:51:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it is already simultaneously complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.90,0:51:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the phone rings
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.90,0:52:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole set is interrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.32,0:52:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be dropped instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.32,0:52:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with no feeling of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.32,0:52:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no feeling of loss
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.32,0:52:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because the sense of completion
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.32,0:52:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,within the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.32,0:52:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the oneness,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.32,0:52:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the unification has already occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.32,0:52:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.32,0:52:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when we come from wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.32,0:52:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.41,0:52:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hold a steak
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.41,0:52:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of a dog's nose
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.41,0:52:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you take it away,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.41,0:52:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he will feel loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.41,0:52:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he will feel grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.41,0:52:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he will feel anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.37,0:52:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In a state of being
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.37,0:52:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,at one with another person,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.37,0:52:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the satisfaction is running simultaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.37,0:52:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.37,0:52:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.37,0:52:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that begins to happen in our life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.37,0:52:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when we let go
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.37,0:52:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of any particular appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.37,0:52:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When we let go of being run
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.37,0:52:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,by any appetite,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.37,0:52:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.37,0:52:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is complete at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.40,0:52:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll notice that with weight reduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.40,0:52:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that if we let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.40,0:52:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappear that hungriness,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.40,0:52:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that wanting of the food,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.40,0:53:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the being run by hunger,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.40,0:53:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.11,0:53:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the sense of wanting to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.33,0:53:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.33,0:53:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,now arise out of the eating itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.33,0:53:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When we sit down to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.33,0:53:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there still is no feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.33,0:53:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of hunger or appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.33,0:53:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But as we begin to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.33,0:53:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the enjoyment is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.33,0:53:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.33,0:53:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the doorbell rings
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.33,0:53:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,right in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.33,0:53:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of eating your steak,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.33,0:53:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you can leave the meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.33,0:53:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,go and be with a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.33,0:53:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no feeling of loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.33,0:53:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,no feeling of lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.33,0:53:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the completion
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.33,0:53:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanies the enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.33,0:53:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of coming
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.33,0:53:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,from a wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.33,0:53:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's always as though
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.33,0:53:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just this side
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.33,0:53:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.33,0:53:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to push the next second.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.33,0:53:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how that is in sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.40,0:53:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how that is with eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.40,0:53:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always anticipating
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.40,0:53:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the next biteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.40,0:53:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're anticipating
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.40,0:53:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the next sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.40,0:53:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always anticipating.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.40,0:53:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're reaching
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.40,0:53:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that there's always
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.40,0:53:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,an internal strain
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:54:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,between what is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.40,0:54:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,right this second
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.40,0:54:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you desire
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.40,0:54:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and want and crave
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.40,0:54:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to happen in the next second.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.40,0:54:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that wanting, craving,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.32,0:54:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,desiring is let go of,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.32,0:54:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening now
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.32,0:54:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is the feeling of being
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.32,0:54:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exact moment
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.32,0:54:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so that each moment
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.32,0:54:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is complete and total in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.32,0:54:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of its completeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.32,0:54:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be stopped any second
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.32,0:54:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with no feeling of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.32,0:54:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in a very
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.57,0:54:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,high energy state,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.57,0:54:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of high energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.57,0:54:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,joyfulness, blissfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.57,0:54:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no feeling of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.57,0:54:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody can turn off
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.57,0:54:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the television set
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.57,0:54:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the program you've been watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.57,0:54:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,no feeling of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.57,0:54:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.57,0:54:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.57,0:54:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of your consciousness now
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.57,0:54:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of coming from completeness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.57,0:54:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.57,0:54:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To be with that person now,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.57,0:54:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to feel it one with their energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.57,0:55:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to feel that acceptance,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.57,0:55:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that aliveness of that oneness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.57,0:55:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is at the very moment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.57,0:55:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of his experience
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.57,0:55:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,already complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.60,0:55:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no have to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.60,0:55:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,continue this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.60,0:55:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because the sense of completion
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.60,0:55:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the anticipated future.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.44,0:55:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure of the eating
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.44,0:55:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the anticipation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.44,0:55:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of the next biteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.44,0:55:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of sexuality then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.66,0:55:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,has an internal strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.66,0:55:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It disallows the expansion
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.66,0:55:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,into the infiniteness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.66,0:55:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which rightfully accompanies
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.66,0:55:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.66,0:55:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go of that desiringness then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.66,0:55:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,allows us to be completely at one,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.69,0:55:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,completely content.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.69,0:55:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Each moment then arises spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.69,0:55:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Each moment seems to be arising
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.69,0:55:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.69,0:55:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the embrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.95,0:55:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience now is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.95,0:56:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though it's a movie unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.95,0:56:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are a participant in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.95,0:56:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are enjoying the unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.95,0:56:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of this spontaneity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.95,0:56:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.25,0:56:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you've owned yourself back as source.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.25,0:56:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of putting it outside of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.25,0:56:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as something to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.25,0:56:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you've owned it as something that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.25,0:56:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.25,0:56:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and your way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.25,0:56:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with that way about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.25,0:56:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience is coming from within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.25,0:56:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there is no gap
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.25,0:56:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,between that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.25,0:56:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.25,0:56:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.25,0:56:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're coming from a lower energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.25,0:56:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like you are here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.25,0:56:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is desired is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.25,0:56:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the desire then is pictured as
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.25,0:56:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow coming across
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.25,0:56:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and reducing the distance and the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.25,0:56:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's always that feeling of space
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.25,0:56:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,between that which you think you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.25,0:57:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.25,0:57:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.25,0:57:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the subject and the object.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.25,0:57:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As we let go of that and become free of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.83,0:57:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then we begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.83,0:57:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,life spontaneously unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.83,0:57:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.83,0:57:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to feel a reverence
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.83,0:57:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for the nature of this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.83,0:57:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Life becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.83,0:57:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is described by the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.83,0:57:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a mystic?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.83,0:57:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystic is a person who has really
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.83,0:57:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,let go of that desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.83,0:57:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and is experiencing from second to second
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.83,0:57:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the completeness, the totality,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.83,0:57:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and in it the exquisite beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.83,0:57:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore a reverence
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.83,0:57:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sacredness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.83,0:57:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore now the relationship becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.83,0:57:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,an expression of that which is sacred,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.83,0:57:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the enjoyment of the exquisite
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.83,0:57:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,sense of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.83,0:57:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it has transcended the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.83,0:57:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How has it transcended the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.83,0:57:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We could say that the world is that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.53,0:58:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which is constantly changing,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.53,0:58:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that which begins and that which ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.53,0:58:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.53,0:58:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that which limits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.53,0:58:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we identify with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.53,0:58:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then it limits our experience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.53,0:58:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to that local wanting, cravingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.53,0:58:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let that go then,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.53,0:58:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that energy field which begins to come
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.53,0:58:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,through the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.53,0:58:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which unites us with that other person
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.53,0:58:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in this spontaneous joyfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.53,0:58:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,means that we've really transcended the world
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.53,0:58:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because now the energy that we're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.53,0:58:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.82,0:58:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes an infinite experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.82,0:58:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about this philosophically.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.82,0:58:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about it experientially.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.82,0:58:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the sexual experience now expands.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.82,0:58:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of a local genital phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.82,0:58:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we notice the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.82,0:58:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.82,0:58:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From the entire body it may now be
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.82,0:58:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to expand to like a space around the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.82,0:58:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be as though the whole room
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.82,0:59:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is having an orgasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.82,0:59:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems as though some kind of an infinite space
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.14,0:59:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.14,0:59:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the body is merely expressing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.14,0:59:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what is happening in that space.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.14,0:59:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The body then becomes like the marionette
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.14,0:59:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which is acting out
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.14,0:59:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going on in an invisible realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.14,0:59:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.72,0:59:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So the energy of this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.72,0:59:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have our survival
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.72,0:59:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on anything that is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.75,0:59:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, we're experiencing that which is unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.97,0:59:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we say that love is unlimited?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.97,0:59:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If we look around us,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.97,0:59:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we see lovingness everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.97,0:59:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The expression of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.97,0:59:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no beginning, it has no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.97,0:59:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.97,0:59:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that limits it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.97,0:59:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is our willingness to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.97,0:59:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our willingness to open ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.97,0:59:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.97,0:59:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an infinite ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.97,0:59:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when we open ourselves up to it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.97,1:00:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,by letting go of that which opposes it,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.97,1:00:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we become an expression of that lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.97,1:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We experience it then as an infinite state
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.97,1:00:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that transcends the personality,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.97,1:00:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that transcends time and space.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.13,1:00:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest aphrodisiac
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.13,1:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is that inner sense of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.13,1:00:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As that aliveness intensifies,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.13,1:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though that sense of aliveness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.26,1:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,awakens all of us,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.26,1:00:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the totality of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.26,1:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That feeling of loveness,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.26,1:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,godness,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.26,1:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is the greatest aphrodisiac of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.55,1:00:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.55,1:00:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the sexuality of the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.55,1:00:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the sexuality of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.55,1:00:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The sexuality that arises out of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.55,1:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And here when we're talking about heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.61,1:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not talking about the physical organ.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.61,1:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about heart
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.61,1:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital H.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.61,1:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart, that which is all-encompassing,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.74,1:00:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is all-diffuse,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.74,1:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is all-inclusive,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.74,1:01:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that intense sense of aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.74,1:01:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the exquisite pleasure
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.74,1:01:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the experience of our own existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.74,1:01:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed now within the energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.74,1:01:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of being with someone
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.74,1:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,whose energy matches yours,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.74,1:01:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,its polar opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.32,1:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to experience in this space then,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.64,1:01:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that opposite within us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.64,1:01:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have not experienced before.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.64,1:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We allow then to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.92,1:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the man his own feminine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.92,1:01:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He then owns it in the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.92,1:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the embrace.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.92,1:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.92,1:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that energy field within herself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.92,1:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,coming back to her through the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.92,1:01:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore there is that sense of oneness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.92,1:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and that completeness,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.92,1:01:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the magic of that embrace.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.92,1:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic of that embrace
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.92,1:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is the joining of these two energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.92,1:01:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the masculine and the feminine,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.92,1:01:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as an expression of their oneness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.92,1:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that intense feeling of aliveness and joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.92,1:02:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles all the problems
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.79,1:02:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that man has talked about
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.79,1:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,having to do with sexuality
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.79,1:02:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because in that inner experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.79,1:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in the subtlety of that inner experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.79,1:02:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is the reconnecting
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.79,1:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with the joy of one's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.79,1:02:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole question about
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.79,1:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,whether God approves of sex,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.79,1:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which is created by the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.79,1:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,by man's left brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.79,1:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what he is asking is,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.79,1:02:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,does God approve of carnality?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.79,1:02:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God approve of that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.79,1:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which is coming out of a negative energy field?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.79,1:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the experience of that aliveness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.20,1:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and that oneness,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.20,1:02:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the experience of joy,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.46,1:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as one moves up to an infinite state
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.46,1:02:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of inner peace and completion,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.46,1:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because completion is peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.46,1:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what is peace but that sense
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.46,1:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of absolute oneness,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.46,1:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the rejoining with the One?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.46,1:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, within that sexuality
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.46,1:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which arises out of the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.46,1:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the return to the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.46,1:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of being with the One
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.46,1:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that gives it its mystical transcendent quality,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.46,1:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,its sense of everywhere-ness,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.46,1:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,its sense of completion.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.46,1:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though it speaks for all men
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.46,1:03:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and for all women for all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.46,1:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner feeling that one is all men
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.46,1:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and all women for all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.46,1:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wondering if one is Adam or Eve.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.62,1:03:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people have had that thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.62,1:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When that sense of oneness comes in,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.68,1:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though one transcends all of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.68,1:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One has been all of men forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.07,1:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One has been all of women forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.07,1:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We own the source.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.07,1:03:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We are that,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.07,1:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of which that experience arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.07,1:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer at the effect of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.07,1:03:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but the expression of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.07,1:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredible sacredness and its beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.77,1:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The subtlety of that inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.77,1:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We look within.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.77,1:04:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we make this practical?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.99,1:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it sound like fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.99,1:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it sound like the mystical, the unreal?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.99,1:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it sound like the sex of unicorns perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.99,1:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not real men and women?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.79,1:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are certain ways in which one can
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.79,1:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,practically move into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.79,1:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to get unfocused
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.79,1:04:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from the physicality and the body
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.79,1:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,arises out of an ancient
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.79,1:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional meditative technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.79,1:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really worth trying,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.79,1:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be amazed at the results.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.04,1:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time when you're having sexual experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.04,1:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,focus your attention and keep it there
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.04,1:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the entire experience
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.04,1:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,one inch below your navel.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.08,1:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.08,1:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a point the Japanese call the hara,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.08,1:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,one inch below the navel.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.08,1:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's used in martial arts
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.08,1:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where one focuses one's centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.08,1:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of paying attention
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.08,1:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the movements of the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.08,1:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of paying attention
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.08,1:04:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the manipulations,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.08,1:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the endless anxieties,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.08,1:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,concentrate, fix your attention right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.08,1:05:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your attention no matter what is happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.08,1:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll find that you're somewhat removed now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.08,1:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this somewhat removed state
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.08,1:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where you become somewhat the participant observer,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.08,1:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire experience now takes on
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.08,1:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.20,1:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is now sort of happening within you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.33,1:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of being focused into the local,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.43,1:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you're experiencing now
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.43,1:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from a more generalized energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.43,1:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that as a way to move
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.43,1:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from that local experience
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.43,1:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,on up to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.65,1:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just move into that point called the hara,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.65,1:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-A-R-A,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.10,1:05:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll notice the change of quality
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.10,1:05:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of the experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.10,1:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll see it's what we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.10,1:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.10,1:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about quality
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.10,1:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because when you move out of the localization,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.10,1:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you're moving into a different energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.10,1:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and the entire experience is then of one of expansion,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.10,1:06:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,an expanded experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.10,1:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,much greater, greater in intensity,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.10,1:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,much more fulfilling,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.10,1:06:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,much more gratifying,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.10,1:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,subsequent to which one feels joyful and grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.10,1:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grateful instead of satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.36,1:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference is gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.36,1:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the energy field of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.36,1:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude is up here about 540,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.36,1:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,akin to joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.36,1:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of satisfaction of desire,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.36,1:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which leaves people often with a sense of loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.36,1:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Latin phrase meaning after intercourse,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.36,1:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there is sadness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.36,1:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why after intercourse is there sadness?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.36,1:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or sexuality without a sexual partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.36,1:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it leave you with a sense of sadness?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.36,1:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A sense of loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.36,1:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was becoming,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.36,1:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as it was coming from that sense
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.36,1:06:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of non-completion,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.36,1:06:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that sense of lack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.36,1:06:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was putting the source of one's sexuality
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.36,1:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,out there someplace in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.36,1:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of reowning it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.36,1:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.64,1:07:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of innocence that arises
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.64,1:07:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then puts you back in the Garden of Eden
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.64,1:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as though you have just
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.64,1:07:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,uneaten,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.64,1:07:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,uneaten
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.64,1:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the tree of good and bad,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.64,1:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.38,1:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though it takes you out of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.44,1:07:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the field of carnality
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.44,1:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and puts you back into the innocence,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.44,1:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness of the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.44,1:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.44,1:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.54,1:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the greatest of all human experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.54,1:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In it,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.30,1:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we demonstrate that whole principle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.30,1:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That it isn't the events of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.30,1:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.30,1:07:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but how we are with those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.30,1:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how we decide to be with that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.30,1:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that determines the nature of the experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.30,1:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a guilt-inducing,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.30,1:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,frustrating,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.30,1:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,anxiety-provoking,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.30,1:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,neurotic type
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.30,1:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of a dysfunction,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.30,1:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether it is one of the greatest
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.30,1:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of all human experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.30,1:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All arises of how we decide
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.30,1:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.30,1:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How we decide to hold that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.36,1:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,within our experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.36,1:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What context we're coming from
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.36,1:08:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about who we really are
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.36,1:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the nature of human experience.
